            <description><![CDATA[
							<h2>New Features</h2>
							<ul>
							    <li>Adds a basic list view</li>
								<li>Adds the ability to remove custom icons from files and folders by dragging them onto <em>Quick</em><strong>Drop</strong> when no icon is selected</li>
							</ul>
							<h2>Fixes and Improvements</h2>
							<ul>
							    <li>Fixes an issue where the settings window was opened by default after launching the app</li>
							    <li>Improves the main window title</li>
							</ul>
							]]></description>
